@startuml Payment_Processing

' ============================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM: Payment Processing
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' ============================================

title Payment Processing - Sequence Diagram

actor "Finance Officer" as Finance
participant "Finance Portal\n(Next.js)" as UI
participant "Reward Service\n(FastAPI)" as Reward
participant "Wallet Service" as Wallet
participant "Celery Workers" as Celery
participant "PostgreSQL DB" as DB
participant "Payment Gateway\n(Telebirr/CBE)" as Gateway
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
participant "Researcher" as Researcher

== View Pending Payments ==
Finance -> UI: Login to finance portal
UI -> Reward: GET /payments?status=pending
Reward -> DB: Query validated reports awaiting payment
DB --> Reward: Payment queue
Reward --> UI: Pending payments list
UI --> Finance: Display payments ($50,000 total)

== Process Batch Payment ==
Finance -> UI: Select reports for payment
Finance -> UI: Approve batch payment
UI -> Reward: POST /payments/batch\n{report_ids: [12345, 12346, ...]}

Reward -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
Reward -> DB: Verify reports are validated
DB --> Reward: Reports verified

loop For each report
    Reward -> DB: Get researcher wallet info
    DB --> Reward: Wallet details
    
    Reward -> Wallet: POST /wallet/credit\n{researcher_id, amount, report_id}
    Wallet -> DB: UPDATE wallet balance
    Wallet -> DB: INSERT transaction record
    Wallet --> Reward: Balance updated
    
    Reward -> DB: UPDATE report payment_status = "paid"
end

Reward -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

Reward -> Celery: Queue payment notifications
Celery -> Notification: Send payment confirmations
Notification -> Researcher: Email: Payment received ($5000)

Reward --> UI: Success (10 payments processed)
UI --> Finance: "Batch payment completed"

== Researcher Withdrawal ==
Researcher -> UI: Login to researcher portal
UI -> Wallet: GET /wallet/balance
Wallet -> DB: Query wallet balance
DB --> Wallet: Balance: $15,000
Wallet --> UI: Balance details
UI --> Researcher: Display balance

Researcher -> UI: Request withdrawal ($10,000)
UI -> Wallet: POST /wallet/withdraw\n{amount: 10000, method: "telebirr"}

Wallet -> DB: Check balance & withdrawal limits
alt Insufficient Balance
    DB --> Wallet: Balance too low
    Wallet --> UI: Error: Insufficient funds
    UI --> Researcher: "Insufficient balance"
    
else Balance OK
    DB --> Wallet: Balance sufficient
    
    Wallet -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    Wallet -> DB: UPDATE wallet balance
    Wallet -> DB: INSERT withdrawal request
    Wallet -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
    
    Wallet -> Celery: Queue withdrawal task
    Celery -> Gateway: POST /api/transfer\n{phone: "+251...", amount: 10000}
    
    alt Payment Gateway Success
        Gateway --> Celery: Transfer successful (Ref: TXN123)
        Celery -> DB: UPDATE withdrawal status = "completed"
        Celery -> Notification: Send success notification
        Notification -> Researcher: SMS: Withdrawal successful
        
    else Payment Gateway Failure
        Gateway --> Celery: Transfer failed
        Celery -> DB: UPDATE withdrawal status = "failed"
        Celery -> DB: REFUND wallet balance
        Celery -> Notification: Send failure notification
        Notification -> Researcher: Email: Withdrawal failed
    end
    
    Wallet --> UI: Withdrawal initiated
    UI --> Researcher: "Withdrawal processing"
end

== View Transaction History ==
Researcher -> UI: View transaction history
UI -> Wallet: GET /wallet/transactions
Wallet -> DB: Query transaction history
DB --> Wallet: Transaction list
Wallet --> UI: Transactions
UI --> Researcher: Display history

@enduml